                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in the determination of the cross",
                "section on oxygen is due to the uncertainty in the",
                "determination of the ratio of the areal densities gold",
                "and oxygen of about 3%, and additionally due to count",
                "statistics of the oxygen peak and the background due to",
                "nuclear reactions with the carbon substrate.  The",
                "statistical error of the Au peak was always <0.5%."
              ]
            }
